{"tid":2254854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光時」曾考慮營運一年後從私人商業機構申請成為社企。","createTime":"2020-10-23T06:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T13:34:31.000Z","uid":124400,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e4dcc5ee417e8ba4a4a71b68b86471dc22c6b7e4","tid":2254854,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:35:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%B2%E5%BA%97-%E5%85%89%E6%99%82-%E9%96%8B%E5%BC%B5-%E7%9B%BC%E6%88%90%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93-%E9%AB%98%E6%96%BC%E5%B8%82%E5%83%B9%E8%81%98%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25BC%25B5-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%25B8%25A0%25E9%2581%2593-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%2581%2598%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%2580%2585%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FREngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=cd9a77a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25BC%25B5-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%25B8%25A0%25E9%2581%2593-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%2581%2598%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%2580%2585%2F&h=e2afb486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%B2%E5%BA%97-%E5%85%89%E6%99%82-%E9%96%8B%E5%BC%B5-%E7%9B%BC%E6%88%90%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93-%E9%AB%98%E6%96%BC%E5%B8%82%E5%83%B9%E8%81%98%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85/</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中運動持續至今，被捕人數以千計，可能有不少人因此失業或須支付大筆訴訟費，面對長遠經濟困難。，一家標榜「利用網購成為一個支援社運的渠道」的網店「光時」昨日正式開業，表示希望能夠為因參與社運而失業的香港人，提供就業機會。「光時」強調，<span class=\"red\"><strong>盈利將全數用以支援香港社運</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n網店「光時」昨日正式開業，販售食品、個人護理產品等日用品為主，貨品價格與市面相若。「光時」在社交媒體公佈，成立目的是希望建立一個可持續發展的就業平台，「不割席亦不施捨」，為因社運犧牲前途的香港人提供就業機會，累積工作經驗，「能夠有尊嚴地活著」。<span class=\"red\"><strong>目前營運團隊約有 50 人，均以非受薪義工形式協助。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n「光時」表示，成立支援社運的企業最早由一名連登網民提出，公司目前有 3 名股東，發起人並無擔任股東、董事及任何有利益相關職位。<span class=\"red\"><strong>「光時」強調會確保盈利每一分一毫都會用在支援社運人士，並考慮營運一年後從私人商業機構申請成為社企。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2019/10/7 &mdash; 17:14<br />\n<br />\n一開始想做社企，一年之後都係覺得做公司好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac9c8c716ab1a671e3b4d0b5a12e75dff8e8507","tid":2254854,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65d979804ac66c34ea9e723f921cc33a3417fbac","tid":2254854,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"過百萬年薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比我都唔轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458b04c2e846af8eee8742c176d2e15a1ca46bec","tid":2254854,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"65d979804ac66c34ea9e723f921cc33a3417fbac","tid":2254854,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"過百萬年薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比我都唔轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:41:50.000Z","msg":"你隻五毛就縮番入去啦"},{"pid":"660f0febc03b404d89062e057ab3525706cbc4fc","tid":2254854,"uid":7482,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開始諗住收支平衡算<br />\n家陣有多就幫埋我供樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  收支唔平衡就唔好意思 為左我層樓犧牲一下大家"},{"pid":"3feaebead77f4733ef1f8f661dfcc0c31e5cde4c","tid":2254854,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"最大問題係光時一開始用左社企模式去運作公司，無問題嘅本來，但而家佢地俾人感覺係想賺錢，成件事就錯灑，話佢地欺騙消費者都唔過份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f289aa83ac6d1ba7707aa281d19be9daf26f4b","tid":2254854,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1b140ceee451ec5a98209cfdbc021abe17db096","tid":2254854,"uid":51422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"本身幫襯開良糧同無名士，大家覺得光時有問題可以轉去其他黃店平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e677fcf37b058ae20294eadd888e4cfc8298e085","tid":2254854,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0f289aa83ac6d1ba7707aa281d19be9daf26f4b","tid":2254854,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3feaebead77f4733ef1f8f661dfcc0c31e5cde4c","tid":2254854,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"最大問題係光時一開始用左社企模式去運作公司，無問題嘅本來，但而家佢地俾人感覺係想賺錢，成件事就錯灑，話佢地欺騙消費者都唔過份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"你都幾樂觀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5530662c6faec2629c6e4cb0417b25e0adb0dc6e","tid":2254854,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eac9c8c716ab1a671e3b4d0b5a12e75dff8e8507","tid":2254854,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"Condom"},{"pid":"4c8880ef1658dce54faf11659b08392d0fbda2ce","tid":2254854,"uid":253